Twitter's VP of Trust and Safety Ella Irwin says she has resigned from the company
The FSB claims Apple helped the NSA hack Russian diplomats' iPhones; Kaspersky: unknown malware leveraged zero-click exploits on iPhones running up to iOS 15.7

Some Apple Savings Account users have had trouble transferring money out of their accounts; Goldman representatives have given differing responses on what to do
